Common Use Cases 
• Customer Support: A bot that reads your specific product manuals to 
troubleshoot user issues. 
• Legal/Medical Research: Quickly finding specific clauses or research papers 
across thousands of PDFs. 
• Internal Knowledge Bases: An AI for employees to ask, "What is our company 
policy on remote work?" 
